    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Enerdusk》</strong> 是一款以单位为核心策略的Roguelike卡组构建游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡牌赋予单位力量，单位的强化反过来进一步增强卡组并扭转战局。利用卡牌和道具的效果来触发单位的技能，掌控战场局势吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/a6e68c422ac028ffb04cc1f8bc5f3d5a.poster.avif?t=1736862603\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/a6e68c422ac028ffb04cc1f8bc5f3d5a.webm?t=1736862603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/a6e68c422ac028ffb04cc1f8bc5f3d5a.mp4?t=1736862603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中，你可以招募各种各样的伙伴（单位），玩家最多可以组成四人的队伍投入战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个伙伴都通过卡牌获取力量，并施展独特的技能。通过卡牌与单位的巧妙组合，找到胜利的契机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/e9704bfdc9551a5f38bd063e6e2c965b.poster.avif?t=1736862603\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/e9704bfdc9551a5f38bd063e6e2c965b.webm?t=1736862603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/e9704bfdc9551a5f38bd063e6e2c965b.mp4?t=1736862603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战斗中，你还可以通过使用背包中的卡牌将新卡牌加入到你的卡组中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一些单位技能能够移除不需要的卡牌，让你在战斗中实现快速调整卡组。这使你能够从精炼的手牌中打出强力卡牌，对敌人施加毁灭性技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/631de0d1d23af2b5ef0bf2c07685a94d.poster.avif?t=1736862603\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/631de0d1d23af2b5ef0bf2c07685a94d.webm?t=1736862603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/631de0d1d23af2b5ef0bf2c07685a94d.mp4?t=1736862603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人通过公开的敌方卡牌对你的单位造成伤害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于敌方卡牌始终可见，攻击、守备还是强化卡组，这些决策完全由你来掌控，战局的发展取决于你的选择和判断。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras/f1cfe1b03d29bf866eabcef14a2eb652.avif?t=1736862603\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302460/extras_big/f1cfe1b03d29bf866eabcef14a2eb652.avif?t=1736862603 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过事件，伙伴可以获得并装备各种道具。找到单位与卡组的最佳组合，打造最强战斗队伍吧！</p>",
